Ryan Kwanten https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ryan_Kwanten 0 Ryan Christian Kwanten (born 28 November 1976) is an Australian actor and comedian. He played Vinnie Patterson from 1997 to 2002 in the Australian soap opera Home and Away. After his stint ended, he joined the American teen drama series Summerland, portraying Jay Robertson. In 2008, he was cast as Jason Stackhouse in True Blood and currently stars in The Oath. Ryan_Christian_Kwanten ( born 28_November_1976 ) is an_Australian_actor_and_comedian .
